481
01:16:13,039 --> 01:16:14,399
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo, mislim, mogu.

482
01:16:14,960 --> 01:16:19,680
[SPEAKER_01] raditi 12 sati na dan, 5 godina, ali 6 godina ne mogu.

483
01:16:20,239 --> 01:16:22,800
